- Include an image prompt, image alt suggestion, and brief editor notes.
- Do not include blog_html. The final fusion model will create the clean semantic HTML.

Return only valid JSON. Do not use markdown fences.

Use this shape:
{
  "generated_title": "",
  "slug": "",
  "meta_title": "",
  "meta_description": "",
  "excerpt": "",
  "image_prompt": "",
  "image_alt": "",
  "blog_markdown": "",
  "editor_notes": ""
}`;
